vote.title: Authorize payment to the Texas Department of Transportation for cost overruns related to the intersection and traffic signal improvements at the following six off-system locations: Webb Chapel Extension and Larga Drive, Duncanville Road and Illinois Avenue, Wheatland Road and Bolton Boone Drive, Lake June road and Holcomb Road, Commerce Street and Griffin Street, and Audelia Road and Royal Lane in the amount of $57,174.64 - Financing: General Fund
